This repository contains a complete UVM-based verification environment for the I2C (Inter-Integrated Circuit) protocol. It includes a master agent with driver and monitor components, constrained-random sequence generation, and a scoreboard for functional checking. The environment verifies key I2C features such as start/stop conditions, read/write transactions, acknowledgment behavior, and signal-level correctness over the shared SDA and SCL bus. Designed for learning and practical RTL verification flow development.